name: Synthesis
description:
Document that certifies the existence of a sentient being.

That which is above is from that which is below, and that which is below is from that which is above.

Chemical mixing is analogous to digital mixing.

The time of the work is the time of the observer.

Exploring form and content, light and shadow, contrast and polarity. 

Ps. These notes are not determinations of meaning but merely refractions of their author's mind.
